      <title>律师警告称，英国工人权利改革将损害多元化招聘</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/uk-s-worker-rights-revamp-will-hurt-diverse-hiring-lawyers-warn</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就业专家表示，英国计划从员工入职第一天起保护他们免遭不公平解雇，这可能会减少来自代表性不足的背景的求职者的数量，政府估计该政策每年可能给企业造成数千​​万英镑的损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/uk-s-worker-rights-revamp-will-hurt-diverse-hiring-lawyers-warn</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 06:44:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
