      <title>马科斯与杜特尔特争执加剧，菲律宾继承人争吵不休</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/top-philippine-clans-feud-spirals-as-marcos-son-hits-vp-duterte</link>
